的<rss version="2.0" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/"><channel><title>医学新闻</title><description>来自 News-Medical.Net - 来自世界各地的最新医学新闻和研究</description><link/>https://www.news-medical.net/<language>英文</language><item><title>与应对技巧和社会支持相关的健康矮个子青年的生活质量、自尊</title><description>费城儿童医院 (CHOP) 的研究人员进行的一项新研究挑战了身材矮小会对儿童和青少年的自尊产生负面影响的假设，发现在其他方面健康的矮小青年中，生活质量和自尊与应对技巧有关以及他们感受到的支持程度，而不是他们身材矮小的程度。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Quality-of-life-self-esteem-of-healthy-short-youth-associated-with-coping-skills-and-social-support.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Quality-of-life-self-esteem-of-healthy-short-youth-associated-with-coping-skills-and-social-support.aspx#评论</comments><guid>https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=315469ee-7846-4d16-9002-c58c6cb52953</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 21:12:35 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2018/7/shutterstock_689215504_aa172f48b2a94017b930750da6a268cf-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Quality of life, self-esteem of healthy short youth associated with coping skills and social support]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>研究人员测试了一种为有成瘾、攻击性行为的人提供心理健康治疗的新方法</title><description>来自罗切斯特理工学院五所学院的研究人员正在测试一种新方法，为患有酒精/毒瘾和攻击性行为的人们提供心理健康治疗。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Researchers-test-a-new-way-to-deliver-mental-health-therapy-to-people-with-addiction-aggressive-behavior.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Researchers-test-a-new-way-to-deliver-mental-health-therapy-to-people-with-addiction-aggressive-behavior.aspx#评论</comments><guid>https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=9fbc8e66-35ad-4bb5-bd28-e6df20cae555</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 21:06:57 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2016/3/Abstract_medicine_background-Hilch-1000_f0a8c263e6e04ed18dfcc5ef27c17907-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Researchers test a new way to deliver mental health therapy to people with addiction, aggressive behavior]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>课桌上的智能手机被证明会妨碍学生的注意力，即使关机也是如此！</title><description>智能手机影响学生的注意力。实验证实，智能手机的存在导致认知能力下降。研究探讨了影响。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Smartphones-on-desk-proven-to-hamper-student-focus-even-when-switched-off!.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Smartphones-on-desk-proven-to-hamper-student-focus-even-when-switched-off!.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=49c51eb9-24a0-41d0-9d09-5ce93204d426</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 20:50:00 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="1333" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/images/news/ImageForNews_750809_16866124784236408.jpg" width="2000"><media:description><![CDATA[Smartphones on desk proven to hamper student focus, even when switched off!]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>太空飞行经历改变人脑结构，对长期任务构成挑战</title><description>太空飞行会影响大脑结构。更长的任务会导致更大的心室扩张，尤其是在头 6 个月内。较短的任务间间隔限制了心室的恢复。调查结果揭示了太空飞行期间大脑的极限和恢复能力。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Spaceflight-experience-alters-human-brain-structure-posing-challenges-for-long-term-missions.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Spaceflight-experience-alters-human-brain-structure-posing-challenges-for-long-term-missions.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=4692476d-6366-4c25-8c01-bd42ed728b12</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 20:39:00 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="1125" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/images/news/ImageForNews_750776_16866167439653346.jpg" width="2000"><media:description><![CDATA[Spaceflight experience alters human brain structure, posing challenges for long-term missions]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>长期接触铅、镉和砷会增加患心血管疾病的风险</title><description>根据今天发表在《美国心脏协会杂志》上的一项新的美国心脏协会科学声明，通过常用的家居用品、空气、水、土壤和食物长期接触低水平的铅、镉和砷会增加患心血管疾病的风险美国心脏协会，美国心脏协会的开放获取、同行评审期刊。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Chronic-exposure-to-lead-cadmium-and-arsenic-associated-with-increased-risk-of-cardiovascular-disease.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Chronic-exposure-to-lead-cadmium-and-arsenic-associated-with-increased-risk-of-cardiovascular-disease.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=2c214e29-4c87-4e2e-a298-aa4bf234972e</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 14:44:00 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2014/9/heart_disease_1_12c3ff20f43b43d898bf18f5689e0c7c-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Chronic exposure to lead, cadmium and arsenic associated with increased risk of cardiovascular disease]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>研究为对激素治疗有抵抗力的前列腺癌提供了一种可能的治疗选择</title><description>前列腺癌是最常见的恶性肿瘤，也是美国男性癌症死亡的第二大原因。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Study-provides-a-possible-treatment-option-for-prostate-cancer-resistant-to-hormone-therapy.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Study-provides-a-possible-treatment-option-for-prostate-cancer-resistant-to-hormone-therapy.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=dcfffc54-6a0f-4fef-b46a-a91b64f86284</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 14:40:31 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2014/7/174318220-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Study provides a possible treatment option for prostate cancer resistant to hormone therapy]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title> Rice U. 博士后研究员探索更年期与阿尔茨海默病之间的联系</title><description>三分之二的阿尔茨海默病患者是女性，但大多数研究都忽略了两性之间的差异。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Rice-U-postdoctoral-fellow-explores-the-link-between-menopause-and-Alzheimere28099s-disease.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Rice-U-postdoctoral-fellow-explores-the-link-between-menopause-and-Alzheimere28099s-disease.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=0710fa0c-e7ae-4506-9bc7-b2d6cfbf43e8</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 14:35:37 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2016/2/Alzheimers_amyloid_plaque_-_Juan_Gaertner_9638f1223d534b518a192c8478871d65-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Rice U. postdoctoral fellow explores the link between menopause and Alzheimer’s disease]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>首创的预后血液测试可以更好地预测先兆子痫风险</title><description>几十年来，医生通常依靠测量血压和尿液中的蛋白质来确定女性是否会患上先兆子痫，这是一种严重的高血压疾病，影响全球大约 2% 至 8% 的孕妇。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/First-of-its-kind-prognostic-blood-test-can-better-predict-preeclampsia-risk.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/First-of-its-kind-prognostic-blood-test-can-better-predict-preeclampsia-risk.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=2186329b-31fb-48ea-a682-bd3fff167e65</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 14:31:20 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2016/3/Blood_Testing_6c4f4bff47c24f5ba754ed98c75bd512-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[First-of-its-kind prognostic blood test can better predict preeclampsia risk]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>促甲状腺素释放激素神经元在对禁食和减肥的反应中起着关键作用</title><description>甲状腺激素 (TH) 水平的调节是一个复杂的多层次现象。下丘脑（控制非自愿神经系统的大脑区域）的室旁核 (PVN) 已被确定为促甲状腺素（一种由脑垂体分泌的调节甲状腺激素产生的激素）的直接调节剂。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Thyrotropin-releasing-hormone-neurons-play-a-key-role-in-the-response-to-fasting-and-weight-loss.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Thyrotropin-releasing-hormone-neurons-play-a-key-role-in-the-response-to-fasting-and-weight-loss.aspx#评论</comments><guid>https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=5ff4a79d-e4e7-4e59-ae8b-cd3c1a8ba9d1</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 14:26:38 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2014/7/Thyroid-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Thyrotropin-releasing hormone neurons play a key role in the response to fasting and weight loss]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>所谓的“孤儿药”为制药公司赚的钱与主流药物一样多</title><description>据西弗吉尼亚大学的一位研究人员称，用于治疗罕见疾病的药物为制药公司带来的收入几乎与向公众销售的药物一样多。法学院教授肖恩·图 (Sean Tu) 发现利润丰厚的所谓“孤儿”药物可以获得制造税收抵免，专利独占期更长，并且更容易受到食品和药物管理局的审查。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/So-called-e2809corphane2809d-drugs-earn-pharmaceutical-companies-as-much-money-as-mainstream-medicines.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/So-called-e2809corphane2809d-drugs-earn-pharmaceutical-companies-as-much-money-as-mainstream-medicines.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=793dd197-6ede-43d2-8670-eaeec4e149f0</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 14:11:00 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2018/7/By_Gorodenkoff_571684e159074a84992c0edbe24d0030-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[So-called “orphan” drugs earn pharmaceutical companies as much money as mainstream medicines]]></media:description></media:content></item></channel></rss>